La Vega J H George Dixon Campus

data.description: This charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with vaulted ceilings exudes a blend of modernity and comfort. The laminate wood-like flooring flows seamlessly throughout, guiding you to a kitchen adorned with quartz countertops and complemented by stainless steel appliances. The elegant bathroom adds a touch of sophistication, while the wooden back porch beckons for tranquil moments in the backyard. Among its highlights are foam insulation, new drywall, double-pane windows, updated electrical, recessed lighting, updated plumbing, hardie board siding, and a tankless gas water heater, ensuring both efficiency and style throughout the space.
